Circle of Steamfront<BR>
Circle of Combines<BR>
<BR>
(I'll guess they get the SoV circles this level also)<BR>
<BR>
At 34 Wizards get these ports:<BR>
<BR>
Combine Port<BR>
Nek Port<BR>
(and the VoS ports)<BR>
<BR>
At 39 druids get this port:<BR>
<BR>
Circle of Misty<BR>
<BR>
At 39 Wizards get these ports:<BR>
<BR>
Common Port<BR>
Ro Port<BR>
<BR>
So basically we get a few of the druids ports levels after they do!<BR>
<BR>
Wizards don't port to Steamfront, Lavastorm, Feerrott or Misty.  Butcher and Gfay are close enough to call them even.  How about evening those things up, give us those ports! at the same level as the druid.  We could call it an even trade and give them the Nek port, seeing how that's the only port wizards have that druids don't.  Then again who goes to Nek anyway?<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
